Package maze

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Maze
    Class to record the details of a maze.
    Tile
    Class recording the details of specific tiles in a maze.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Maze.Direction
    Enum to represent the different directions
    Tile.Type
    Enum to represent the different types for a tile.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidMazeException
    Class to throw an exception if the maze is not a valid maze.
    MultipleEntranceException
    Class to throw an exception if the maze is not a valid maze because it has multiple entrances.
    MultipleExitException
    Class to throw an exception if the maze is not a valid maze because it has multiple exits.
    NoEntranceException
    Class to throw an exception if the maze is not a valid maze because it has no entrance.
    NoExitException
    Class to throw an exception if the maze is not a valid maze because it has no exit.
    RaggedMazeException
    Class to throw an exception if the maze is not a valid maze because it is not rectangular.
